n lumas will detect and block the malicious activity what download speed can luma support our luma wifi routers utilize the ac wireless network standard on the backside of the luma you will also see  ethernet ports which are able to handle speeds up to  gbps gigabit per second that means you will have the latest wireless standard as well as the fastest download speed around your home how does ‘content filtering’ work luma accesses a vast variety of databases to base content filtering on and is constantly monitoring traffic for inappropriate content how do i set a bedtime restriction for a user the bedtime feature gives luma administrators the ability to set bedtime rules for individuals on the network a bedtime schedule can be set per user for the entire week or just certain days during the selected bedtime period the user will have their internet access paused until the set awake time all products covers studio apartment – up to  sq ft for small homes  apartments – up to  sq ft covers most homes – up to  sq ft luma in the press luma a router that provides a boost to internet speed and security luma is designed to bring wireless networking to all parts of your home luma offers a mesh network to ensure even coverage ratings  reviews   luma home inc all rights reserved features specs faqs reviews add to cart contact us – luma surround wifi luma guardian support buy now contact us contact usmark russellt phone   email email protected mail po box  atlanta ga  luma homecareers legal press privacy policy warranty product infoalexa luma guardian specs  design store luma communitycontact us install setup support   luma home inc all rights reserved luma guardian support buy now buy – luma surround wifi luma guardian support buy now buymark russellt luma  whole home wifi  pack   get the fastest wifi anywhere on all of your devices all at once keep your kids out of harm’s way and set content filter ratings at the network level lock down your home internet with enterprisegrade 