ort   luma home inc all rights reserved luma guardian support buy now atlanta startup jobs  vp of product management toggle navigationatlanta startup jobs home contact resources remote jobsjob alertsbackvp of product managementluma home incstartup location atlanta ga luma home inc – vice president of product management with the rise of the connected home people are using more devices than ever home wifi networks now need to be able to keep every one of them running and fully secure the team at luma home has decided to use their expertise to create the perfect personalized wifi network for everyone  luma’s mission is clear to deliver to each customer’s home the fastest simplest most secure and most reliable home network that’s equipped for the technology of today and tomorrow  you can learn more about us at wwwgetlumacom     main role responsibilities strategically advise and collaborate with the executive team on the vision of the product and the company  be exceptionally productminded constantly thinking of innovation and improvements from customers’ perspective  own the full product management lifecycle – gathering requirements from a broad spectrum of stakeholders  internally working closely with engineering marketing and sales and externally working with customers analysts domain thought leaders and continually accessing competitive capabilities    writing detailed product requirements that clearly define the features to be developed by the engineering team and ensuring that the delivered product meets the needs of customers while the role will have an externalevangelical component it will be more focused on defining and executing the product roadmap  have the visioncapability to help the company transition from a one productone market organization to a multiproductmultimarket company  help to identify future investment and market opportunity establish discipline around requirements gathering product prioritization schedulesdeadlines output and requests  desired skills and experience    proven success in a fastpaced startup environment with a handson “roll up your sleeves and grind it” approach  prior experience managing a team across multiple product lines handson experience being able to effectively interact with multiple constituencies including engineering marketing sales and external customers expertise in product home connected market  handson experience managing building and motivating a worldclass global product management organization experience leading a business team successfully through rapid product proliferation and market platform expansion  rigorous product management background with rich experience managing product roadmaps and defining product prioritization based on business goals capacity to bring positive energy and enthusiasm to a team and help the product management team establish credibility within the broader organization  experience managing release schedules in the context of an agile development environment bachelor’s degree in a technical field  personal qualifications strategicbig thinker and visionary who can create and develop the longterm product vision willing to work directly with a small fastmoving smart team and able to work in ambiguous and rapidlychanging growth environment smart collaborative and able to communicate clearly  looks to “seek the truth”  not a pontificator  talks through difficult issues with colleagues and make decisions based on evidence and argument not ego  decisive in complex business situations  cool under pressure  has sufficient maturity and experience to recognize and react quickly to unexpected opportunities and challenges a resultsoriented motivating leader who can lead teams positively influence peers and superiors and deliver great products and outcomes can motivate persuade and challenge subordinates and peers to achieve desired results can balance the use of deadlines accountability and positive reinforcement for superlative team performance metricsdriven able to translate strategy into measurable operational goals and objectives disciplined in assessing performance and addressing problems rigorous in delivering results and in holding team members accountable for their own results highest ethics integrity and intellectual honesty possesses a strong sense of selfconfidence and unquestioned integrity with a strong sense of personal ownership and responsibility in accomplishing the company’s product and overall vision and goals luma is committed to building a strong team that is connected to and helps strengthen the culture of our company we have a cool headquarters in midtown atlanta located in a great central location  we offer a competitive total pay package which includes stock options discounted health benefits paid holidays and vacation and more        luma is surround wifi that brings home internet into the modern era with a focus on speed safety and security luma empowers users with visibility into their home wifi system and control over their family and home network’s safety you’ve never had wifi like this to apply for this job email your details to email protected apply using webmail gmail  aol  yahoo  outlook ×closedo you want to know about the latest atlanta startup jobsread atlantas hottest startup job postings in your inbox bizapediacom  human validation companiespeopleproductsservicestrademarksaddressesphone book our system has detected a high number of page requests from your ip address please prove to us that you are a human to continue using our website please send me to the search subscription offer page after i successfully answer the word challenge bizapediapro searchperform unlimited searches via ouradvanced search form withbizapedia pro searchfind out more bizapediapro databuild custom data listsfor one or many stateswith bizapedia pro datafind out more  copyright   · bizapediacom · all rights reservedblogpro searchpro apicontact usterms of useprivacy policysitemapdesktop version luma menu how ca